CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

April 12, 2005

[Cite as 04/12/2005 Case Announcements, 2005-Ohio-1702.]

DISCIPLINARY CASES

2005-0066. In re Resignation of Huegel.

On affidavit of resignation from the practice of law of Allison K. Huegel, Attorney Registration No. 0039630, and on report filed under seal by Disciplinary Counsel.

Resignation accepted.
